      <title>参议员表示，美国应考虑对欧尔班领导下的匈牙利实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/us-should-weigh-sanctions-against-orban-s-hungary-senator-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国一位高级议员称匈牙利总理欧尔班·维克多为“最不可靠”的北约盟友，并提出实施制裁的可能性，暴露了人们对这位东欧领导人日益增长的愤怒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/us-should-weigh-sanctions-against-orban-s-hungary-senator-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 11:16:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
